Package: isofracDH
Title: Tidyverse Tools for Hydrogen Isotope Fractionation Calculations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Carolynn", "Harris", email = "carolynn.m.harris@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tidyverse-native functions for calculating hydrogen (D/H)
    isotope fractionation and mixing relationships described in Sessions (2005),
    with teaching-oriented examples and visualizations.
